title: SAMP server (including Pawno)
description:
SAMP server (including Pawno)

The full set to get your SAMP server started.(You still ned an Hamachi Network)
Including the script program PAWNO to help you script your server/Gamemode.
The package also includes some gamemodes like:
Las Venturas Deathmath
Sniper(Deathmatch)
Money Grumb
And some other Gamemodes

Install notes:
1 Unrar
2 Edit the .CFG file.(Open with Wordpad)
3 Start your server or start scripting with PAWNO
4 Have Fun


Note: If you want to play on your lan server just add :[Port number]

Example:   :7777 or :7778


Problems? visit www.sa-mp.com or send me a message.

I will be seeding 24/7 but it would be nice if you guys seeded some too :)
